OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSweeping changes urged to  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fhelp Church abuse survivors
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Church of England safeguarding measures
OL,6, against sexual abuse fall below the    
OL,7, standards expected of secular          
OL,8, organisations, a report has concluded. 
OL,10,FIt says most abuse survivors surveyed  
OL,11,Fwere not satisfied with the outcomes   
OL,12,Fwhen they engaged with the Church.     
OL,14,FOne recommendation is for two new      
OL,15,Findependent charities funded by the    
OL,16,FChurch to take over the protection of  
OL,17,Fchildren and vulnerable adults.        
OL,19,FThe report will be discussed at the    
OL,20,FGeneral Synod this weekend.            
